# Cursor Project Rules — AI Crypto Market Intelligence Platform

This document is the **source of truth for AI agents (Cursor, ChatGPT, Claude, etc.)**
working on this repository. It explains the architecture, coding standards, and rules
for implementing new features.

The goal is that **any AI agent reading this file can immediately understand the system.**

---

# 1. Project Overview

This project is an **AI-powered crypto market intelligence platform**.

It aggregates:
- real-time market data
- crypto news
- AI analysis
- narrative detection
- historical similarity insights

and presents them through an interactive dashboard.

Main capabilities:

• Real-time market monitoring
• AI-generated market brief
• Token-level analysis
• Narrative detection
• Ask-AI interface
• Historical similarity (RAG)
• Voice briefings

